// equivalent of header file in C/C++
// `declare` specify type of an existing variable that can be referenced (i.e. module to import here)
// i.e. concretely used so YCM/tsserver won't complain when importing *.png image
// see: https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/modules.html#wildcard-module-declarations
declare module '*.png';
